        <h3>About coins</h3>
        <p>Coins are a digital currency used on Decate. They are purchased via SMS (there are plans for credit card payments in the future). Here are some general terms regarding coins. Note: The general site vilk√•r for bruk still applies to coins, this is just an additional page</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Coins are used for purchases on the Decate platform itself and may or may not be used elsewhere.</li>
            <li>Decate coins are not redeemable for cash and are non refundable. Decate does not accept cancellations or offer refunds under any circumstances in whole or part thereof once payment of the original purchase has been made and the coins are issued.</li>
            <li>Your coins are not guaranteed and in case of system failure or the site being closed are not refunded in any way, shape or form, including but not limited to digital currencies, Decate coins, cash, products, gift vouchers or anything of the sort. This also applies if you delete your account, are banned from the site or in any way, shape or form lose your coins or access to them.</li>
