            <li>We reserve the right to give you coins or take them away at any time, for any reason. Removing your coins are mainly done in extreme cases.</li>
            <li>Your coins may be charged at any time by our system and charges are non-refundable. In cases where a feature auto-charges itself (a monthly VIP feature, for example), it will automatically charge you at the designated period automatically. It's your responsibility to make sure that undesired features are not set to auto-charge you.</li>
            <li>When purchasing coins, you must be over 18 years of age or have the authorization of an adult responsible for either you or the form of payment used. It is your responsibility to make sure of this, as all purchases of coins are final. If you are under 18, it is the responsibility of your legal guardian to be fully aware of your purchase and the terms attached to it.</li>
